MOTUS!!!
for Linux and Windows!

Availiable Modes:
UK-English 8 char (no accents words)

Guess an eight letter word, using correct letters as clues: you are given a list of your correct letters and the position of those in the right place. For example:

Word to guess:	increase
Player guess: 	imported
Correct:		i-------
misplaced:		re

All the words are stored in .dic files

...you could use try using grep.